• How does the code in the test program work?

  First, it made an array called animals and set the array size to 3.
  second,fill the array wuth calling dog and cat classes with their name in the constructer.
  then, initialize integer i as zero.
  when i is less than the length of animals array. it will call the method in introduceYourself() in each Animals child class array. then, Add +1 to i.
  next, repeat until value of i is greater than the length of the animals array then stop.
  
• How does an array work?

  when i is less than the length of animals array. it will call the method in introduceYourself() in each Animals child class array. then, Add +1 to i.
  next, repeat until value of i is greater than the length of the animals array then stop.
  
